OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FShowery
OL,6,Frain will move east on Sunday. Cloudy
OL,7,Fon Monday with some rain later.
OL,8,FTurning rather wet and windy on
OL,9,FTuesday. Temperatures slowly
OL,10,Fincreasing near to average.
